name: Fighub chart
description:
Let's play with Figma with some of the new features (Interactive Components + Variants + Auto Layout) that I combined to make this Github style chart.


You can use it as a drawing board to click out the patterns you want.


Duplicating and Remixing are welcome. 😁


Anyway，I ❤️ Figma.


---


拿 Figma 近期出的几个新功能（Interactive Components + Variants + Auto Layout）组合一起练手小临摹了一下 GitHub 的 Contribution Chart。


可以拿来当画板点出自己想要的图案哦。


欢迎复制玩耍和 Remix 魔改 😁


Anyway，I ❤️ Figma.
